[[File:Anzat_feed.jpg|thumb|right|250px|An Anzat attempting to extract the "soup" from [[Quinlan Vos/Legends|Quinlan Vos]].]]
{{Quote|The blend of what you are and what you will be.|[[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[T'ra Saa/Legends|T'ra Saa]]|<ref name="Star Wars (1998) 34">[[Star Wars (1998) 34|''Star Wars'' (1998) 34]]</ref>}}
"'''Soup'''" was the term [[Anzat (species)|Anzati]] used for the brain matter and mental essence of [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]], which they consumed as food. The concept of the soup was developed from early Anzati legends about [[Silent Voices|the aurora]] that surrounded [[Anzat/Legends|their homeworld]], which they believed to be the life forces of their ancestors.

